com.nimsoft.nimbus
Class NimAddress

java.lang.Object
  com.nimsoft.nimbus.NimAddress

public class NimAddress
extends Object

Container class to hold information about a Nimsoft bus address. Nimsoft bus addresses are in the form: 

 /domain/hub/robot/probe
  • domain: the Nimsoft domain (unrelated to Windows domains)
  • hub: the Nimsoft hub (typically the unqualified machine name)
  • robot: the Nimsoft robot (typically the unqualified machine name)
  • probe: the name of the Nimsoft probe
Instances of this class are immutable and therefore safe to share between threads.
